OL,3,CGrandad stuck in Dubai for almost a
OL,4,Cweek 'just wants to be home'
OL,6,FAs more flights from the Middle East
OL,7,Fstart to bring people back to the UK,
OL,8,Fa grandfather from Oxfordshire says he
OL,9,Fhas been left in limbo.
OL,11,FBarry Wagner from Henley and his
OL,12,Fpartner were due to fly back from
OL,13,FDubai five days ago.
OL,15,FThey are among around 138,000 British
OL,16,Fnationals who have registered their
OL,17,Fpresence in the Middle East, as many
OL,18,Fwere left stranded in the region
OL,19,Ffollowing the outbreak of the US-
OL,20,FIsraeli war on Iran.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
