OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772917925
OL,3,CGrandad stuck in Dubai for almost a
OL,4,Cweek 'just wants to be home'
OL,6,FThe first government-chartered flight
OL,7,Fcarrying Britons left Oman's capital
OL,8,FMuscat on Thursday (5 March).
OL,10,FMeanwhile, a commercial British
OL,11,Fairways flight will take passengers
OL,12,Ffrom Muscat to London Heathrow today
OL,13,F(Saturday 7 March).
OL,15,FMuscat, which is some 300 miles by
OL,16,Froad from Dubai and Abu Dhabi, has
OL,17,Femerged as a key location for people
OL,18,Fto leave the Middle East.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
