OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772917925
OL,3,CGrandad stuck in Dubai for almost a
OL,4,Cweek 'just wants to be home'
OL,6,FBarry says him and his partner have
OL,7,Fhad three flights cancelled and say
OL,8,Fthey are being given little
OL,9,Finformation as to when they can return
OL,10,Fhome.
OL,12,FMr Wagner said: "I'm hearing people
OL,13,Fthat were due to go home yesterday,
OL,14,Fmay have actually got home, but other
OL,15,Fpeople that have been stuck here since
OL,16,FSunday, are not getting on some of
OL,17,Fthose flights.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772917925
OL,3,CGrandad stuck in Dubai for almost a
OL,4,Cweek 'just wants to be home'
OL,6,F"You just don't know what's going to
OL,7,Fhappen. The biggest fear is the debris
OL,8,Fcoming down from the interception is
OL,9,Fwhat is most scary.
OL,11,F"You just want to be home. I want to
OL,12,Fsee my family. Want to see my
OL,13,Fgrandchild. You know, just just
OL,14,Fdesperately want to be home."
OL,16,FThe UK government has been criticised
OL,17,Ffor not providing enough military
OL,18,Fassets in the Middle East -
OL,19,Faccusations Downing Street has
OL,20,Frejected.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
