PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1772917925
OL,3,CGrandad stuck in Dubai for almost a
OL,4,Cweek 'just wants to be home'
OL,6,FAddressing the scrutiny at the press
OL,7,Fconference, Starmer said: "I want to
OL,8,Freassure all the British public about
OL,9,Fthe action that we're taking while the
OL,10,Fregion has been plunged into chaos.
OL,12,F"My focus is on providing calm, level-
OL,13,Fheaded leadership in the national
OL,14,Finterest. That means deploying our
OL,15,Fmilitary and diplomatic strength."
OL,17,FThe war in Iran has left hundreds of
OL,18,Fthousands of British citizens stranded
OL,19,Fin the Middle East, as airspaces are
OL,20,Fclosed across the region.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
