OL,6,FAffected British nationals are urged
OL,7,Fto stay up to date with the latest
OL,8,Fupdates from their airline or tour
OL,9,Foperator and review their travel
OL,10,Finsurance policies before travelling.
OL,12,FClick here for more information on
OL,13,Fwhere it is safe to travel and what
OL,14,Fyour rights are.
